# text: So this poses a huge economic challenge , because say you do come up with your great drug or your great vaccine -- how do you deliver it in a place where there 's no roads , there 's no infrastructure , there 's no electricity for refrigeration to keep things cold , there 's no clinics , there 's no clinicians to deliver these things where they 're needed ?
